  "title": "SQL injection in user lookup endpoint",
  "state": "open",
  "locked": false,
  "body": "The `user_lookup` endpoint is vulnerable to SQL injection. It builds SQL queries with f-strings and can be exploited via the `name` parameter.\n\nExample vulnerable code:\n```python\ncursor.execute(f\"SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '{name}'\")\n```\n\n**Bounty:** $100",
